							<h1>Welcome to DoTogether</h1>
							<a href="/activities"><button class="button">View Activities!</button></a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="carousel-item">
						
						<img class="d-block w-100"  src="https://www.colorhexa.com/f69279.png" alt="Why?"style="height: 100vh;">
						<div class="carousel-caption" style="position: center; top: 15%;">
							<h2>Why?</h2>
							<p style="font-size:2em;text-align: justify;">Not everyone has friends and family who share their interests or have flexible schedules. This isolation has become more prevalent due to Covid-19. Therefore, we created DoTogether, a platform that allows users to connect over virtual activities! Finding your activity buddy is only a few clicks away :)</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="carousel-item">
						<img class="d-block w-100" src="https://www.beautycolorcode.com/54d4f3-2880x1800.png" alt="How?" style="height: 100vh;">
						<div class="carousel-caption" style="position: center; top: 15%;">
							<h3>How?</h3>
							<h4>[1]</h4>
							<p1>Sign up!</p1>
							<h4>[2]</h4>
							<p1>Explore posted activities, or post one yourself :)</p1>
							<h4>[3]</h4>
							<p1>Connect with other users and become activity buddies!</p1>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
					<span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
					<span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
				</a>
				<a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
					<span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
					<span class="sr-only">Next</span>
				</a>
